Interface MsgParsable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    InetCon, StreamConI
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileCon, GroupClientCon, GroupClientHub, GroupServerCon, StreamCon, StreamConReader, TcpCon, TcpHandshakeCon

    public interface MsgParsable
    Interface that should be used if something parses or converts a MarkupMsg to it's raw form.
    Since:
    1.0
